      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i just feel like i've been doing everything right lately. my diet is super consistent and i'm exercising way more than before. it just feels like a lot of unnecessary chemical when everything is stable. if my blood work has been fine lately, isn't there a point where you can taper it down safely without waiting for a formal appointment?",
